    "title": "The dictator of Europe has fallen. The Hungarian autocrat and his corrupt mafia-...",
    "description": "The dictator of Europe has fallen. The Hungarian autocrat and his corrupt mafia-style regime have been defeated by the Tisza Party. I've spent nearly eight years of my life in Hungary, and I can truly feel the joy amongst ordinary Hungarians as they've kicked the Orb\u00e1n cabal out of power. Orb\u00e1n's defeat is also a hard slap in the face for Trump. Despite all the trouble he's caused in the world order, Trump sent his own deputy to campaign for Orb\u00e1n in Hungary just days before the election \u2014 a highly unprecedented move. Tonight, I'll raise a toast for my friends in Hungary. Hajr\u00e1, Magyarorsz\u00e1g!",
